      <h1>Getting Started</h1>
      <p><strong>Installation guide:</strong> Install the Multiuploader Chrome extension and connect your account to the Django backend.</p>
      <p><strong>Configuration:</strong> Set marketplace credentials, create upload profiles, and define field mappings for each target platform.</p>
      <p><strong>Upload workflow example:</strong> Choose files → map fields → run bulk upload → monitor status and history.</p>
      <p><strong>Note:</strong> The backend manages file status and progress, while the extension handles platform-specific form automation.</p>
